-- Toshiba Wants Tokyo Electric to Join Turkish Nuclear Bid, Yomiuri Says
-- B y   Y u r i y   H u m b e r
-- 2010-12-31T02:31:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-31/toshiba-wants-tokyo-electric-to-join-turkish-nuclear-bid-yomiuri-says.html
  Toshiba Corp . wants to bid for a
contract to buld a nuclear power plant in Turkey with a group
of companies, including Tokyo Electric Power Co., the Yomiuri
newspaper reported, citing an interview with Toshiba President
Norio Sasaki.  Toshiba may seek financing for the project from the Japan
Bank for International Cooperation, according to the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
